76561198070992254,Recommended,245170,24083233,"Posted: 4 July, 2016",all,Sonicexcel,"Now i bought this game and all its DLC while it was on the steam sale so i got this for pretty cheap compared to what it is normally but will say i do not regret buying this game. This game is a very fun and very polished fighter compared to most Triple A fighters like Street Fighter or Mortal Kombat.Pros:-Very fast Fighting mechanics Similiar to Killer instinct.-Good Training and tutorial for those new or Casual Fighting game players.-Single, Tag, and Triple Team options for matches both offline and Online.-Online Net code is pretty stable.-Lobby play for streamers that want to play with viewers. Up to 8 man lobbies with Everyone can watch 1 match OR all can play their own matches.-Fluid and stylish Animations for characters.Cons:-Story mode for each character seems Rather short and lacking a lot of background or backstory for most characters like Filia, and Ms. Fortune.-Small roster 8 total characters if you dont buy the DLC 15 total with all the DLC-2 DLC characters are reskins of 2 established characters with different move sets. Fukka = Filia, Robo Fortune = Ms. Fortune-Some odd hitboxes for some characters like Peacock's Hat hit box is a little off centered due to her animations and Valentine's hit box spreads through the space separating her legs.Overall i say this game is worth the price and the additional characters are worth looking at but i can only say i recommend this game to casual players as this game doesnt have a very big roster that competitive players like. especially compared to like fighters like Guilty Gear, Street fighter, and Killer instinct."
